The CEO of PMR Africa, Mr Johan Hattingh, handed over the Diamond Arrow to Editor, Tobie van den Bergh. The Middelburg Observer came first after a provincial survey was done on companies or institutions who have achieved the most in stimulating economic growth and development in the province. The winners were chosen by a panel made up of CEO’s, MD’s, business owners, company directors, managers and government officials based in Mpumalanga.
PMR Africa is a consultancy and research company based in South Africa. •The purpose of their award ceremony is to create a platform where companies and institutions can be branded as entities with growing potential.